<br />
&quot;It will be rated R and we are working on a script right now, and Ryan&rsquo;s overseeing a script right now,&quot; Feige told Collider about Deadpool 3, while adding some bad news: &quot;It will not be [filming] this year. Ryan is a very busy, very successful actor. We&rsquo;ve got a number of things we&rsquo;ve already announced that we now have to make, but it&rsquo;s exciting for it to have begun. Again, a very different type of character in the MCU, and Ryan is a force of nature, which is just awesome to see him bring that character to life.&quot;

